All material changes are documented in a sub-form named "Material Changes," which is accessible on the Section record. This form contains the date of the change, the type (e.g., 07 - Change in "Country"), the previous value, and the updated value. By having this sub-form, users will be able to easily view and report on changes, which is not possible with a History Log. 

For the mapping dashboard, two fields are available: "Material Changes Since Last Confirmed" and "Date of Last Material Change." The first field lists all material changes since the last confirmation, not just the most recent one.
